WEBVTT

00:00.133 --> 00:02.800
- (AIR HORN BLOWS)
- (LIVELY CHATTER)

00:02.802 --> 00:06.304
What kind of pledges are
you wimps, huh? Everybody up!

00:06.306 --> 00:10.407
It's 1:00 a.m., boys. That's the
shank of the evening. Let's go!

00:10.409 --> 00:13.113
Let's go! Come on, go for a walk.

00:13.138 --> 00:15.872
Drink! Drink! Drink! Drink!
Drink! Drink! Drink! Drink!

00:15.874 --> 00:19.042
- (WHOOPING)
- All right!

00:19.044 --> 00:20.410
- Drink up! Drink up!
- (LAUGHS)

00:20.412 --> 00:23.913
Drink! Drink! Drink! Drink!
Drink! Drink! Drink! Drink!

00:23.915 --> 00:25.648
(CHANTING CONTINUES)

00:25.650 --> 00:27.283
Drink! Drink! Drink!

00:27.285 --> 00:29.018
(WHOOPING)

00:29.020 --> 00:30.687
(GULPS)

00:30.689 --> 00:33.857
(WHOOPING)

00:33.859 --> 00:35.859
That's number five, baby!

00:35.861 --> 00:37.293
- Yeah!
- All right!

00:37.295 --> 00:38.394
- Let's go!
- Yeah!

00:38.396 --> 00:41.364
Don't you fall asleep, you pledge pukes.

00:41.366 --> 00:43.766
The more you cough,
the more you're gonna get.

00:43.768 --> 00:45.168
Into the water, pukes.

00:45.170 --> 00:47.837
- Let's go! Let's go.
- Come on. Let's go!

00:47.839 --> 00:49.138
(WHOOPING)

00:49.140 --> 00:50.173
In the water. Now!

00:50.175 --> 00:51.241
Wayland, what are you doing?

00:51.243 --> 00:52.609
Move it. Let's go.

00:52.611 --> 00:53.810
Let's go. Let's go.

00:53.812 --> 00:56.746
(GRUNTS)

00:56.748 --> 00:58.248
(COUGHS)

00:58.250 --> 00:59.482
(INDISTINCT SHOUTING)

01:01.486 --> 01:03.253
Hey, you okay? Excellent!

01:03.255 --> 01:05.111
LOGAN (OVER MEGAPHONE): What's all
the talking and laughing about,

01:05.113 --> 01:07.257
pukes? Are you enjoying this?
'Cause you're not supposed to

01:07.259 --> 01:09.192
enjoy this.

01:09.194 --> 01:11.194
Why don't you go swim to the
other side of the lake, huh?

01:11.196 --> 01:14.030
That'll take some of the fun
out of it for ya.

01:14.032 --> 01:15.865
- All right.
- Let's go.

01:15.867 --> 01:18.034
Come on, come on.

01:18.036 --> 01:20.770
LOGAN: Swim faster! Keep going!

01:20.772 --> 01:22.705
Yeah!

01:22.707 --> 01:24.874
(ECHOES): <i>All right, boys.</i>

01:24.876 --> 01:26.809
(BIRDS CHIRPING)

